description: Went to the Pig with Cali in the morning– sat upstairs and talked, then went home. LIly called, we caught up, and then called Nanny/Pop Pop with Dad. Katy and I went shopping, then back home and rested for a bit. Then to dinner in Chinatown with Mom and Katy at a hot pot place. Drove to Clare’s after for my birthday celebration! Guin, Clare, Annika, Steven, Theo, and Penelope there. Cake, Scattergories, gifts, etc. Went home, bed.

Woke up late, went to Sofia’s (gave my birthday gift- books!). Then we went to get coffee/chat at Cafe Mustache. Then to facial, then home, dinner, knit, and went on a drive with Nolan and Sofie. Ended up at Devil Dawgs across the street from Jones. Then Nolan and I went to Oliver’s with Cali, Graeme, and Lydia (Oliver’s ex). Drove home with Cali, knit, and watched the last episode of Bojack.
Lazy day by pool/in room, kitting/reading/swimming in ocean. Sushi for dinner with Howard and Robert. Bed.

Read by the pool with Katy, Mom, and Dad. Then to the airport and plane home (just with Katy, Mom and Dad stayed a bit longer). Plane ride uneventful. Had a small drink and chat with Katy’s friends who came over for wine night.

Woke up, had breakfast, made a patch for Adina. Went thrifting with Penelope at Irving/Kedzie, then to La Boulangerie after for coffee and croissants. She showed me her demos for the record in the car. Stopped by Felt to get jeans, came home and had a quiet night in alone, packing for New York.

Woke up, packed a little, and wrote Sofia an emotional letter. Then went over to theirs. We went to the yarn store and to get tacos. Then back to their to hang out before the Lifeguard show at Shubas. Free photo booth– lots of pictures. Caught up with Asher. Went back to sofia’s for a long talk and a sad goodbye. Home and sleep.

Made a hearty breakfast for myself, how nice. Went to Brooklyn to drop off film, Lily came along. Then we went to bagel bros and talked for a while. Then to class– made friends with the guy sitting next to me. On the way home I ran into that person who complimented my shoes in the cafeteria yesterday. Chatted and followed each other on Instagram. Went home and ate with Elle, lazied around for a bit. Went to Cali’s to eat ramen and watch Nathan for You. Then home and sleep.

Woke up and went to UC for breakfast– ran into Adina on the way and chatted with her. Walked to Michael’s to get yarn for project. Then back home for lazy morning crocheting. To UC for coffee before class, ran into Tessa. Then to class, chatted with two of the kids there. Then lunch before a long studio class. After class I went to dinner at Kimmel (NYU dining hall) with Penelope. Then home and for a rest. Went out and bought a pack of cigarettes to stoop. Back home, shower. Then Elle and Adina came in and we chatted for a while.

Woke up early and walked over to PJ dorm to take pictures. Hung out with her and Sofie for about an hour, then went home and edited/crocheted. Went to class, then back and got more work done. Went Back to the UC to take pictures of gloves with Elle, had dinner there after. Ran into Lily and Milan and then to Cali’s. Emotional night. Things are changing. Went home, talked to Elle. Neighbors were so loud we went to talk to them, but ran into Sage and Oz in the hallway and chatted with them instead.

Woke up and caught up with Elle about the night before, went to get bagels with Paul and Lily. Back to take pictures for class, then to the UC for a snack (ran into Tessa again, chatted for a bit). Both classes fine/normal. Chatted with my professor about punk music after class on walk home. Went home and did work. Then Adina came over to hang with Elle and I. They tucked me in and I went to bed.

Woke up and knit. Went to Mud to do some work– it was semi successful. Went to class, found out Pigeon got the same tattoo as me. Back from class, took photos of Elle– semi successful. Waited around for a while. Went to Chinatown with Lily to take pictures, got caught jumping the turnstile. Went home and did a little bit of work, waited for Elle, talked, and went to bed.

Top of the morning, went to Trader Joe’s. Then at dorm for a while before class. Ate lunch with Della and Milan between my classes. Didn’t do much in class really. Came home, then Adina came over. Hung out with her for a while, made dinner, then knit and to bed.

Woke up early to watch movie, then to Blick again. Back to work on the window, then met Lily to take pictures off the Lorimer stop. Back, got David’s and did a bit more work. To class and back to get more stuff done. Then to Eleanor’s to take photos. Came home, worked, etc. Dropped off clothes at Sachi’s and then hung out at Cali’s for a bit. Back home to finish up project and to bed!

Got bagels at David’s with Lily to discuss Montreal. Back to dorm before going to shoot photos with Cali at NYU studio. Fancy lights. Skipped class, then home to grab project and to studio to present project. Went well. Home and Adina came over to watch TV. Felt bad about Cali. Elle home and talked too. Packed for Providence and to bed.

Went to get a nice pierogi breakfast at Veselka with Cali. Then to came over to hang with Elle and I before my class. To class and back. Spent evening finishing up video project for Time. Adina over to watch TV and help me edit. Small crisis over video, then Elle home and to bed.

Up at Cali’s and then back home to shower. Got David’s and a Covid test. Negative. Did a bit of work before heading to class (chatted with Tessa and Ophelia in dining hall). Boring class. Lunch with Milan before studio. Met Sofie after for dinner at the UC with Paul, Martina, and Adina. Ran into Rosa among others. Got home, felt yucky, chatted with Elle.

Up early for no reason. Still sick. Watched short movie for class and knit. Then did drawings for class. Got dressed and to class ever so briefly. Back and did work. Zoom call with my professor about project. Lazy evening here. Called Dad. Adina came over to hang out. Watched some survivor with Elle and Adina, the early night to bed.

Woke up and got an early start. Went to get film at Luster then left for the Guggenheim. That was a flop– ended up at the Met which was really nice. Stopped into a church on the way home. Got a bagel at Tompkins and then dropped stuff off and walked to class with Cali. Class and then home. Didn’t do anything, really. Sachi came over for dinner and catching up. Was really nice. Then Adina came over/Elle came home and we chatted for a bit. Then I went to bed.

Made breakfast (set off fire alarm) then to work. Dropped off camera, ran into India– made plans for coffee– then to talk to professor Paul after his class (with Martina). Back to dorm briefly before QR. To class and back. Lazied around for a while. Cali came over, we talked, then she left and I did a bit of work. Then I went to Sachi’s for dinner. Chatted with Aidan and Oliver as we made dinner. Maite came later– had wine and talked for a while. Headed home. Late night with Elle doing work before sleep.

Forgot this day to be honest. Knit and did a little work before going to class. Lunch with Paul/Devlin/Gigi/Will before studio. Presented photos– went over really well. Went to have dinner at the apartment with David/Shannon/Ellie. Super nice, got leftovers sent home with me. Back and hung out with Elle, and then to 2L to see Adina (+Kristen) before the trip. Then back up and to bed.

Up and breakfast. Then met Penelope to go thrifting in Bushwick– got some hits. Home and did a bit of work. Got Kristen’s guitar from her room. Then Lily/Paul/Sachi came over for dinner. Chatted/listened to music/played Scattergories– was very sweet. Everyone but Lily left, she stayed and we played guitar together for a couple hours. Then to bed.

Up early to make the bus to Boston out at 9:30. On bus sat next to Lily– the ride didn’t feel very long. Mostly just listened to music and looked out the window. Made it there and went to Maud’s place. Got food, then went to the Isabella Stewart Gardner museum. Wandered a bit and then got dinner (pizza). Back to Maud’s, watched Harry Potter, and then to bed.

Up and did a little work + felting before class! Then to class briefly– tattoo time in Prospect Park afterwards! Tugboat Tattoo– cute dog and beautiful apartment. Then back home to do a little more work that I had been putting off + more felting. Adina/Ava/Kristen came by for a bit, then bed.

One day out and I already am forgetting about what I did. Woke up and did some work, I’m sure. Elle made us french toast which was sweet and yummy. Then to class and back home for a check in on Zoom. Walked around and did some work for class. Then kept working until it was time to see Cali. Stooped and then hung out at hers. Slept over.

Up and feeling gross. To Walgreen/Cvs to get prescription and medicine. Home for breakfast/reading/a bit of work on essays for NYU. Met Cali for coffee at Outro, then to class. Home after, briefly, then to shoot things for class. Chatted with Sage in the hall before walking around Alphabet City and by the river. Home and tired. Quiet evening reading/making dinner/watching TV/listening to music/drawing.

Up early to register for classes– sort of went poorly. Elle got us David’s for breakfast. Read and did some work here. Then went to return camera, lunch at UC, and briefly chatted to to advisor (random one) about registration– all fixed. Yay Then to class, lunch with Adina after  (with Aghill and Della briefly). To class. Snack after class, ran into Maite while heading to tapestry workshop. Couldn’t find classroom– went home. Finished book and brainstormed/internet stalked. Elle home, chatted, and went to bed.

Woke up early to get camera– ran into Lily on the way and got breakfast with her. Home briefly before heading back out to meet Sofie for bagels at Bagel Bob’s. Sat in Wash, then met Lily and Itao in Wash for a while (Edward + others too). Then to class– boring– and home. Did some work before going to NYU dining hall with PJ (ran into Gigi on the way there). Ate in Wash. So nice after! Cali’s after (stoop) then to home and to bed.

Up and did a little work. Lily over to help film something for class. Hung out here for a bit before going to class. Lunch with Eleanor, Bella, and others. Was mid– go to church next time. Then next class– was boring. Home/dinner. Then walk with Paul. Sat by the river and chatted. Felt comfortable and important. Home. Cried a lot about Levi. Lily over to hang out (Elle home for some of it). Lily home and to bed.

Woke up early for breakfast with Paul before his 9am. Ate at UC  then walked home. Did some work at home, then to meet Cali for breakfast at Thai Diner. Yummy. Stopped into a mass on the way back– walked around and then to class. Brief. Lunch after class– meeting with Amy for studio. Back home and helped Viv shoot in our room. Talked to Mom for a bit. Then Cali over. Got snacks for movie night (ran into Itai), then watched movie. Cali home and I to bed.

Up/breakfast/return camera. Cali stoop– anxious still felt really bad. Then back homestill feeling bad. Met her again at some point to try sorting out. Then to class. Church stoop in between. Boring class– let out early. Home + exhausted. Then tried to hype myself up for DJ set. Went with Adina/Ava/Elle. Talked to lots of Parsons people there. Left early w/ Adina to go to Carmelo’s. ID taken! Boo! Home and to bed.

Woke up/UC breakfast? /did work? Finished movie and then met Cali to get David’s. Back and to hand in the dorm with Cali and Elle before going to class. To Blick after class, then worked on project. Then work + dinner at deli with Adina. Watched movie then bed.

Woke up + UC breakfast. Home to work on stuff (script + gargoyle), then to class. Stooped/David’s with Cali before she left for the weekend. Zoom check in with Amy. Then Maite/Sachi/Adina over to felt (Ava + Elle briefly). Then to bed.

Up and to UC for breakfast. Dropped off film with Lily and Itai, then back to do work in the library before class. Back after, work more, then Cali over to do work together and eat dinner. Then she went home and I to bed.

Up and to work! Went to get David’s for me and Elle, then UC lunch with Adina/Ava/Anders. Home to shoot before classes. Guest speaker in studio– Dean Haspies. Dinner at NYU dining hall with Penelope after. Then home. Felt like shit. Talked to Adina/Elle in the room for a bit before bed.

UC breakfast with Adina + Lily. Back, didn’t do much, then met Cali to go rock climbing in Brooklyn with Tess and Aitana. Skipped class, got a salad, came home and rested. Shot final scenes of short with Adina and Lily, then took photos of 2L. To bed!

Finally got a good sleep in. David’s with Elle and Adina. Worked on gargoyle, then coffee with Itai and Lily. Went to UC for lunch, ran into Paul. Class boring. Home to rest + Zoom check in, then back to school for dinner w/ Adina (+ Luna briefly!). Library w/ Adina (did work + goofed off). Home briefly, ten to a restaurant/bar with Adina and her parents (BJ Novak spotting…). Talked to her dad about music. So awesome. Home + to bed.

This day sort of lost to time. Did work on gargoyle in the morning. Then class– NYU acceptance! Yay. Home– wrote email– then shoot with Viv and Elle. Brought them dinner. Then Adina over to do nothing. Bed.

Up and to the UC for breakfast– then went to Cali’s to get some work done! Productive. Went home, then went to school with the gargoyle! Class (QR)– final presentation (mid). Then early to studio to fix the gargoyle. Critique during class (went well)– then dinner at dining hall with Adina. Home– hang with Adina/Della/Ava/Lily/Elle/Freida in 2L. Then to bed.

Up + cafe with Sachi and Elle. Goodbye Sachi! Lots of packing at dorm– watched movies + Lily came over to hang for a bit. Then Lily/Elle/Itai + I to Little Poland for dinner. To Eleanor’s roof after to say hello/bye to friends. Talked to Gigi and Othandiwe a lot. Then back to dorm to finish packing. Goodbye Itai! Said goodbye to Freida and Della after dumpster diving in the Stuy basement. Slept in 8G01 (Celia’s bed) with Luna because Elle had so much packing to do. Last night in dorm.

Up at Shannon/David’s– breakfast/chat with Aunt Shannon before ubering to airport w/ Elle! A goodbye with her before getting on the plane. Uneventful ride home– met mom to take train home w/ all my baggage. Then home + dinner! Drove to pick up Cali to get ice cream. Then home + to bed.

To Cali’s in the morning! Went to First Slice for coffee/pie then ate them in the park. Hung out at hers for a while, then went to meet Penelope + Clare for thrifting at Irving + Kedzie Village Discount. Tacos after with them. Met back up with Cali for a drive home. Then home + rest. Watched a documentary + knit. Chatted with Mom, bed.

Up and met Cali at the Apple Store, lol. Some tension there, then back to hers (stopped at First Slice again). Hung around and watched 500 Days of Summer. Then back to mine w/ her to change. Then to Lincoln Hall for Hallogallo Fest! Chatted w/ Eli, Pigeon, PJ, Clare, Braeden, etc. Lifeguard and otters played– awesome. To Jeni’s after with those guys + Lifeguard. Cali drove many home, then me. Then to bed!

Up early for onboarding call for work (with Sofia). Then to pottery class at Penguin Foot in Logan. Got better at throwing. Dropped off film after at Bellows, then home to rest + get some work done. Drove to Clare’s to meet her, Amelia, Guin, and Penelope for dinner/hang at Clare’s. Drove home and to bed.

Up and to the train! Dropped off key at Theo’s then met Cali at First Slice. Got snacks and got mat from hers, then went to Montrose Beach. Camped out there + read/chatted for a while. Then home + work + knit. To bed.

Adina day! Got up and showered before meeting her, Sara Tweed, and Claire Wennink at Kopi for breakfast. Hung and chatted there for a while, stopped into a little shop before heading out. Dropped off Adina in Logan while I went to do my pottery class. Picked her back up and went to Sultan’s for lunch afterwards. Came back home, rested for a bit, then walked around Lincoln Park for a bit. Mom drove Adina and I to Guin’s for Guint. Steven, Theo, Guin, Amelia, Clare, Liv, and Cali. Fun night there, then home and to bed.

Up and to work as per usual. Then went to Mrs. Reade’s retirement party– very emotional for some reason? Chatted with Eleanor Brady, Mrs. Terrasi, Ms. Bax, and Mrs. Reade. Then to pottery for open studio. Came back home and then Cali came over for a movie. Drove her home (tense) and then back/bed.

Up and to work, shower, and more work. Biked to pottery in the rain, class, biked back in the rain. Did more work, had dinner with Mom and Dad, then to game night at Steven’s with him, Theo, Clare, Liv, Amelia, and Esme. Liv drove me home, then bed.
Up + work. Then went to Cali’s to hang + watch terrible reality show. Got Banh-mi. Then home/dinner, talked to Dad, watched TV/knit with Mom, bed.

Did work in the morning before going to the last pottery class. Small class today, was nice. Met Sofia after at their new place, chatted there, got coffee and walked around. Then I biked home. Ate dinner with Mom before Cali came over. Talked, watched terrible show, then drove her home. Bed.
This day I forgot to write down in my JSON file and I don't have my notebook on me to update it. If you have found this day congratulations! You may smile and laugh.

Slow morning with Elle before picking up Steven to go to Kopi. Theo met us there. Had a sweet time with Elle. Brown Elephant + record store after, then Elle and I to Village Discount. Home (time for me to do work), then Cali, Elle, and I got Potbelly’s to bring to the lake with Steven and Olivia. Terrible air quality! But was still a nice lake picnic. Went to Theo’s after (Clare + Amelia too)– introduced everyone. Then Katy picked us up and we crashed.
Totally forgot what happened this day– went to pottery to trim my pieces. Did work, etc. Then home/dinner, talked to Dad, watched TV/knit with Mom, bed.

Up and out! Went to get Katy gift. Back and some work, then to Pigeon’s to do pottery on their wheel. Chatted with them and their friend Reese. Home, hang, guitar, beer pong briefly with Teddie + Morgan + their friends. Then bike up north to meet Ari + friends at beach. Picnic + chat, (lake with Hudson– sweet) then biked home alone. Really beautiful– fireworks going + me listening to music. Home/shower, TV with Mom, cut my bangs, bed.

Dad left early to go to Maine (Nanny + Pop Pop) – said goodbye. Then breakfast + work. Biked to a few places to try to find Cali gift but to no avail. Got film and lunch (for Mom and I). Home + lazied around– had productive day doing chores/etc. Watched TV a lot in the evening, felt blah. Dinner + TV with mom, bed.

This day I cannot remember. Lots of rain. Fake ID arrived– did work, played guitar, etc. called Cali I think. Went to Guin’s to smoke with her, Liv, and Esme. Talked to her dad in the kitchen for a while. Home + bed.

Days passing quickly. What did I do today… I worked and played guitar as I do but not sure what else otherwise. Dinner (ordered in) with Dad and Katy… then drive to pick up Clare from work. Her work ran late so I wandered around Wicker Park killing time. Then we drove to Annika’s to meet her/Liv/Steven/Amelia/Theo. Went to lake– we got in spontaneously and swam in our underwear. Then back to Annika’s. Drove Liv home, then me home.
Up and on a ran, then back home to do…something…I don’t think I did much this day. Just work and what not..totally forgot what happened actually…oh well.

Anxious day. Did work, called Cali. Tried to go to Clare’s but my way of getting there got messed up and I devolved into an anxiety attack so i just went home. Called Lily on the way back which made me feel better. Walked Charlie, did work, bed.

Woke up fairly late after managing to fall back asleep a few times. Breakfast of banana peanut butter sandwiches. Car still wouldn’t start. Hung around campsite after being on phone with Steven’s dad and waiting for Triple a. Annika, Theo, Liv and I went for a walk while Steven and Clare went w tow truck into town. We walked to the lake, got ice cream, and chatted by the beach. Headed back, then Clare and steven back with working car. Got ready to go swimming! Walked to lake, swam on small beach (dog beach…ha ha). Was beautiful and warm. Steven swam to the other side and scared us all. I read on the shore. Back to camp to make dinner. I showered. Read. Sat by fire + smores. Bed.
Up and for a run. Then a tad bit of work before heading to Ari’s to hang/work together. Went to Target/grocery shopping with them. Then home/hang/more work. Nothing else today I can remember.

Slow day at home, alone working. Played around on the guitar and such. Got very restless and went for a bike ride to the ledge after dinner. Was really beautiful by the lake, journaled for a bit. Will miss biking + Chicago.

Up very early to go to the dentist. Spent a while there (just slow moving), but talked to the woman working behind the desk about New York and sports. The dentist’s daughter and I have mutuals in New York. Then home + work. Slow afternoon. Took the train up to Kimball thrift for one last trip before I go back to New York. Home, work, dinner, Mom back from Lolla, we watched TV, bed.

Up early to finish packing + have slow morning before airport. Said goodbye to Mom, Dad drove me to airport. Flight delayed, spent 3 hours just working there. Finally got on the plane– babies all around me. Taxi to apartment where I met Elle and her mom. Unpacked a bit, got pizza from place on the corner and ate on the roof. Then I went to Cali’s to spend the night there. She left me snacks! TV then bed.

More running around to get things. Started at Cali’s– got a bagel for breakfast. Got my bed frame and night stand. Mattress delivered as well. Got a terrible falafel sandwich for dinner. Nothing too remarkable today. Slept at Cali’s.

Not sure what my morning was. But went in the late morning to meet Sachi to go to the flea market (dropped off film first though– roll was a bust. I hadn’t loaded it correctly). But Sachi was going through something with Eli so I went alone. Hot walk, blisters, and the place was closed when I got there. Ugh. Home, then Sachi came over. Chatted with Elle, then just Sachi and I got lunch and walked around Williamsburg. Went to Muji + Trader Joe’s. Then we parted. Went home, then back out to get Super Taste for Cali and I! Met her at her place, caught up, watched John Wilson, then bed.

Up and unsure what. Went to Cali’s to hang before she had to go to work. Chatted with Julia’s friend Zoe, watched video essay, and went to the deli to get a snack. I went home and she went to work. Lily arrived at the apartment. Caught up with her which was nice, then we all went to Muji. Home, ate dinner on our floor– how sweet. Then I hung around until Cali got done with work. Went to hers to spend the night. Bed.

Had a lovely slow morning here with Cali. Made coffee + breakfast and played Bananagrams. Then she went home. I helped Lily carry up her bed frame and then went to meet Liliana and Brett at Little Poland. Had lunch and talked for about an hour which was really sweet. Then went back to Brooklyn, got a pepper plant, (tried to) help Lily build her bed frame (which was broken). Chloe, Addie, and Ava over before going to show with Lily. Talked to them for a bit– they’re sweet. Helped Elle carry up her dresser, then caught up about the night before (she had had someone over). I made dinner, then went to Adina’s. Sat in Tompkins with everyone + 2 Brits who hadn’t left yet, then home. Watched TV with Mom, played guitar, bed.

Woke up to rain– beach day cancelled. Did a but of work before going to meet Cali for bagels by her place. Then we took the train up to the Moma and spent a couple hours wandering around there. Was lovely! Back to hers– talked about our friendships with other people which quickly devolved into me having an anxiety attack. Calmed down and we both headed to my place. I did work and we listened to a (true crime) podcast. Anderson + Sarah over briefly. Then Cali and I hung for a bit longer before she left for Pigeon’s. I did work and ate dinner, then Lily got home and we played guitar together for a while. Bed.

Another 9am! Got bagel/coffee at the deli and ate on the way to class. First class was Interaction– teacher seems awesome. Sarah/Lily in my class. Ate solo lunch on church steps after class, then sat outside Parsons building. Chatted to Keir and his friend. Then saw Bella before next class. Space with Aviva. Ade friends with the freshman next to me, weird moment with Aviva, but that’s all. Went home then grocery shopping. Back home, felt weird. Did a bit of work, went for a walk. Went to Penelope’s late (trains being weird + she didn’t send me address till late). No one answered the door. I waited. No answer. Left, called Mom and Dad. Talked to LIly when home, was comforting. She, Elle, and I talked for a bit when Elle got home. Then bed.

Woke up and went to Cali’s to drop off stuff. Weird vibe. Talked for a second, still weird. Then home + breakfast (+therapy set up). Back to Manhattan to do risograph orientation. Sat outside school, called Clare for a bit, killing time before dermatologist appointment. Ran into Mick on the way there, very sweet! Then the derm. Rain into Gigi/Oliver on the way back. Then home, did some work. Chatted with Lily and Cabe came over briefly. They left. Paul came over. We caught up and made coffee. Lily back briefly, talked with Paul, then she left again. I made dinner for Paul and I which was really lovely. Had a wonderful time. Freida, Adina, Della, Ava (+Lily/Elle) over (Paul left). Chatted, played bananagrams, made silly song for Della. Bed!

Day off I spent most of the day inside doing work or putting said work off. Worked on silly Space project, did readings, etc. Called Theo on the way to Bakeri, was nice to catch up with him. Then I got focaccia for Paul and I! Met him at his place and then walked to the park to eat it. Went back to his to hang for a bit, then I went home to make dinner. Can’t remember much of anything else that happened. Lily came back from her crazy date, she filled me in.

Woke up at Cali’s, then headed home for quick intake meeting for therapy. Laundry, some homework, some work. Lazied around, then Cali over. We talked for a bit (+fashion show for party tomorrow). Then we went to get fun fish ice cream. Then to Spectacle to see movie. Was good, director was great + really nice. Home, heavy chat about her tendency to talk about other people (what fun!). Then talked to Lily about it when she got home. Bed.

Up w/ Cali, slow little morning before she left for class. Then I made breakfast and went to get tattoo! Flower (peony) on my arm. Hand poked, covered up the tooth. 6 hour session! But was good, didn’t feel crazy long. Went home after, made dinner and rested for a bit. Then met Cali at Irving Plaza to see Melt Banana! Had some beers in the park first to kill some time. Awesome show, was very fun. Downsides was not much of the instrumentation was live and a shorted set because they were opening. Went home after (parted ways with Cali). Ran into Ezra (chatted for a second). Bed.

Had a sweet little morning in with Lily and Elle. Went to Paul’s to hang and mend pants. Then home and Cali over to do interviews for her class about her– was tough to do given everything. Lily’s bandmates– Riley and Ava– came over to practice. Listened to them. Then went to Slowdive. First time going to a show alone– felt so normal. Left before the encore– ran into Lulu on the train back. Then home/bed.

Up and a sort of numb feeling about Cali. A sense of relief. Maybe a sign the break should be official. Talked to Lily for a while, then met Paul and went to the park. Sat up on the rock, then the beach as I sewed. Talked about Cali and Lily. Then home to get the nice light to shoot Lily in. Adina over (she + Elle brought me coffee)! Had a quick shoot, then everyone gone after a bit. Lily brought Gigi over briefly. Lol. Worked on my gloves for a bit. Then went to Black Spring to help Itai buy stuff for the event that night. Filled in him about what was happening. Then home to do a little more work. Then back to Black Spring for a poetry night. Was lovely, talked to Tess a lot, it was really nice and a good moment for our friendship. Talked to Devin and Alex too, etc. Then Tess and I walked home– they needed to charge their phone. Martina was over for dinner with Lily, all four of us hung out for a while. Tess left– I talked with Martina and Lily for a bit after– again, a really nice conversation. Then bed.

Big day. Got up, breakfast. Then straight to doing homework to keep my mind busy. Was pretty productive. Then got ready– scary. Met Cali in Tompkins. We talked for a long time (+ran into Pigeon). We broke up. Was so emotional and sad. Hard to tell if it was the right decision– seeing her made it so hard. I love her a lot, missed her a lot over that week break. It was really nice to see her. Feeling conflicted. Went home. Spent a lot of time on Instagram. Paul + Lily came over for a debrief and dinner which was nice. Sent them away (kindly) and spent some time alone. Was so exhausted so I went to bed early.

Thursday day off. Up and did some work, stopped by the post office, then met Ari to climb. Was fun, we also lifted for a second. Then got tacos + took train. I went to print, they went to meet Leni. I printed posters for class (big! 27x39in). Then to Bushwick to try on climbing shoes (no luck). Then home. Did a little work, then when to Paul’s to meet Sam! Talked with them (+Lily) over dinner, then went home and to bed. Exhausted.

Spent the morning in, I think. Watched videos for class while carving a spoon out of wood. Lazied around some more, then went to the pottery studio. Very successful throws! Yay!
